extendedInfo.description: This is special version of Moe Moe Battle!At first, you and enemy choose two of attack from four kinds.At second, you and enemy choose one of attack from the two.The damage is changed by kinds of attack.ex.	Fire : Wind = heavy damage!	Fire : Water = lite damage...	Fire : Fire = no damage!?If you choose same kinds of attack twice, the damage is heavier than normal attack!You have to know what kind of attack is effective to the enemy.You need strategy!Can you read the mind of enemy?
